Get free icons in Papercut design style

Papercut is one of our bright decorative icon packs. With their unique layered texture, they instantly grab attention in a sea of generic icons. Whether you're designing a website, mobile app, or presentation, Papercut icons fit right in.


Download free Papercut icons in different categories for your UI and graphic design needs. These free graphics are pixel-perfect and are available in PNG and SVG formats.


Also, check Doodle, Color, and Gradient icon styles.
